Posts.Content: I found these boards looking for fellow Stage IV surviors and was thrilled to read some of your stories. Ive been dealing with this for five years, but its not the "Cancer-free anniversary" that some get to have. Its nice to know that there are other people out there who have taken all the same drugs I have....Kathy! Ive seen the business end of all those needles - NO FUN! Im glad there are others out there who have taken their "new normal" and still seem to stay positive and believe, like I do, that the possibilites are endless....
Posts.Title: Stage IV Breast Cancer Survivors?
My doctors wont take me seriously because I am so young.
